descriptionHtml:
RR Skyrim Seifuku for UNP v2.01


[Introduction]
 This MOD adds Blazers & Skirts & Accessories

 
[Contents]
 Blazer                     20colors
 Skirt(Calves)              24colors
 Ribbon(Amulet)              7colors
 Necktie(Amulet)             7colors
 StrapRibbon(Amulet)         5colors
 Shoes & Socks               4colors
 Shoes $ KneeSocks          18colors     
 

  These are equipment equivalent to "Leather equipment".
  These production and strengthening are almost the same as "Leather equipment".


[Installation]
 overwrite Meshes and Textures folder,and esp file /Skyrim/Data/
 and activate esp file.


[Location]
 Entrance of Whiterun town.
 These enter the chest near the rampart.


[Notice]
 If you use the old version, please install the new version
 after that's uninstalled.

 
[At the end]
 Please use these when good though these are not so good.
 The modification and the re-distribution of these files
 are prohibited.
 I wish to express my gratitude to Skyrim and you.
 Enjoy!


 Presented by Reira
